				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466333#post-1438636</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466333/scp-1771#post-1438636</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 May 2012 06:26:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>SoullessSingularity</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>637830</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I would like here to note that the inspiration of this SCP is from a newbie in a chat who mentioned something about a house which had people swap according to the seasons. Said newbie disappeared and hasn't appeared in many, many months and I found the initial premise interesting so I took my own spin on it. If you are the newbie who mentioned the idea and don't like how it's being used, let me know and I'll remove it accordingly.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
